            "- Enables authentic, real-time brand communication (e.g., live product launches, behind-the-scenes access).",
            "- Students can create and broadcast their own shows to fellow students — educational applications.",
            "- Creates a sense of immediacy and exclusivity — audiences must tune in live to see the content.",
            "",
            "Productivity Tools: Social media tools designed to enhance an organisation's productivity by supporting social event management, scheduling, data collection, and cloud-based workflows.",
            "",
            "Examples: Doodle (scheduling polls), SurveyMonkey (online surveys), Google Alerts (monitoring mentions), Google Docs (cloud documents and spreadsheets).",
            "",
